WEBVTT

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.639
When you fall lower from a low.

00:02:30.640 --> 00:02:34.719
For me, it was when lots
of my pilots got rejected.

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:38.519
Honestly, no channel wanted to meet me.

00:02:38.520 --> 00:02:40.949
How many chances will we give
Jeetendra’s daughter?

00:02:41.760 --> 00:02:45.559
Some media professionals saw
those pilots with my father,

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:51.199
and one of them asked "Are you putting
your money into your daughter’s hobby?"

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:53.799
Now only actors understand

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:57.399
that in every actor’s life,
there is something called a facade.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:59.199
Even if he is broke,

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:03.599
if due to bad investments or family
disputes he has little money,